# GROUNDED Nodes — install command redirects (Netlify / Cloudflare Pages format)
#
# Each Node's install one-liner points at a clean URL here; we redirect to the
# raw install script in that Node's own repo. curl -fsSL and PowerShell's irm
# both follow redirects, so a 302 is enough — the script downloads the app itself.
#
# Add two lines per new Node.

/analytics/mac      https://raw.githubusercontent.com/pauldevelopai/node-analytics/main/install.sh   302
/analytics/windows  https://raw.githubusercontent.com/pauldevelopai/node-analytics/main/install.ps1  302
